OL,3,C'Without the RSV she would have lived
OL,4,Clonger' - mum urges others to have
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,FBut for some babies and and older
OL,8,Fpeople with underlying illnesses it
OL,9,Fcan be much more serious.
OL,11,FRumer's mother Helen Roper said: "She
OL,12,Fspent 6 weeks in intensive care so she
OL,13,Frecovered from the RSV but it had
OL,14,Fdamaged her lungs which were already
OL,15,Fcompromised so much that she couldn't
OL,16,Fcome off the ventilator.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
