OL,3,C'Without the RSV she would have lived
OL,4,Clonger' - mum urges others to have
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,F"They tried something called non-
OL,8,Finvasive ventilation which is like a
OL,9,Fmask which worked to a degree but in
OL,10,Fthe end she just couldn't not come off
OL,11,Fa ventilator and her organs started to
OL,12,Ffail and she died early on new years
OL,13,Fday in 2016."
OL,15,FShe continued: "It was the RSV that
OL,16,Fcompromised her lungs which meant that
OL,17,Fshe did not live as long as she
OL,18,Fpossibly could have and we didn't have
OL,19,Fthe chance to manage the apnea which
OL,20,Fwas really quite minor.
