OL,3,C'Without the RSV she would have lived
OL,4,Clonger' - mum urges others to have
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,F"She'd been discharged from NICU, she
OL,8,Fwas well, she had minor treatable
OL,9,Fproblems and then she caught RSV and
OL,10,Fshe was back on a ventilator.
OL,12,F"Without the RSV she would have lived
OL,13,Flonger and that was the case for the
OL,14,Fother children in that hospital."
OL,16,FHelen is herself a midwife and said
OL,17,Fthat even she didn't know much about
OL,18,Fthe condition before her daughter
OL,19,Fcontracted it.
