OL,3,C'Without the RSV she would have lived
OL,4,Clonger' - mum urges others to have
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,F"I think I'd vaguely heard the name.
OL,8,FAs a midwife it's not something that
OL,9,Fcrosses your mind", she said.
OL,11,FToday, over 75s and some pregnant
OL,12,Fwomen in Wales can now get a
OL,13,Fvaccination against RSV.
