OL,3,C'Without the RSV she would have lived
OL,4,Clonger' - mum urges others to have
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,FDr Chris Johnson, Consultant
OL,8,FEpidemiologist at Public Health Wales,
OL,9,Fsaid: "The vaccine's being offered in
OL,10,Fpregnancy for those who are 28 weeks
OL,11,For over and getting vaccinated during
OL,12,Fpregnancy passes some of those
OL,13,Fantibodies onto the baby and allows
OL,14,Fthem to be protected for the first few
OL,15,Fmonths and the first year of their
OL,16,Flife when they're at the highest risk
OL,17,Fof being hospitalised or being
OL,18,Fseriously ill.
