OL,3,C'Without the RSV she would have lived
OL,4,Clonger' - mum urges others to have
OL,5,Cvaccine
OL,7,F"But we're also able to offer it to
OL,8,Fadults after their 75th birthday and
OL,9,Fthat will really help reduce the
OL,10,Fburden on the healthcare service and
OL,11,Fthe burden of distress on the families
OL,12,Fof those people becoming seriously
OL,13,Fill, ending up in hospital and
OL,14,Funfortunately sometimes dying."
